Package: investlabr
Title: Research Workflows for Macro and Cross-Asset Analysis
Version: 0.0.4.9
Authors@R: person("Oliver", "Zhou", email = "oliver.yxzhou@gmail.com",
                 role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reusable research workflows for macro-financial and
    cross-asset analysis. The package sits on top of data packages such
    as 'investdatar' and focuses on transforming existing market and
    macro data into analysis-ready research tables, factor and indicator
    constructions, event and regime overlays, sensitivity estimates,
    scenario comparisons, and research-grade visualization outputs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/OliverLDS/investlabr
BugReports: https://github.com/OliverLDS/investlabr/issues
